data.description: OPEN HOUSE 12/2/23, 12:00pm-3:00pm.    We want to welcome you to your future home in the heart of San Antonio's vibrant Southtown area!     Settled in this historic neighborhood, our charming 1915-built house has undergone a remarkable transformation. Our vision?  To blend the timeless elegance of a bygone era with modern comforts and conveniences, and it's now ready to greet its new owners with open arms.    The original external architectural features have been lovingly preserved, including the spacious porch that can accommodate outdoor seating, creating an inviting and warm atmosphere.     Our dream for both bathrooms was to give you a spa-like ambiance, where you can unwind after a long day in your very own oasis of relaxation.     One of the standout features of this property is the integration of smart home technology. We've installed a Ring Camera surveillance system, ready for you to set up and enhance your peace of mind, ensuring your new home is as secure as it is stylish. The house is also equipped with Ring doorbell, a Google Nest programmable thermostat, and Google Nest x Yale door locks on the front and back doors.  Additionally, this house comes with 2 Google Nest minis.       We know it's not just the house itself that makes this property special, it's the community. Southtown is an up-and-coming neighborhood that's brimming with life and culture. Explore the local art scene, savor mouthwatering cuisine at nearby eateries, and stroll through the charming streets to discover hidden gems around every corner.     This house offers endless possibilities for creating cherished memories. We believe this lovingly remodeled 1915 gem in Southtown is a testament to the perfect blend of history and modernity. It's more than just a house; it's an opportunity to become part of a thriving, diverse community while enjoying the comforts of a thoughtfully renovated home. Don't miss your chance to make this vision your reality - schedule a viewing today and let your journey to Southtown living begin!
